data.description: ***Assumable Interest Rate 2.875****Welcome to your new home at Gardenia Way! The location can't be beat for your commute to Seattle, PSNS or Bangor. You're near the ferries and just a hop and a skip to freeways, shops and restaurants. Step inside to the vaulted entry of this casually elegant home & you'll be impressed with the warm & welcoming feel & the great room layout. Adding to the sense of generous spaces are 9ft ceilings throughout the home. The great room features built-in media shelves and a cozy gas fireplace. The gorgeous kitchen features custom cabinetry and quartz countertops. Enjoy a relaxing soak at the end of a long day in the spa like owner's suite. This newer built home features white painted doors & trim & amazing deck!
